Package: doncoind
Architecture: any
Depends: +ACQAew-shlibs:Depends+AH0-, +ACQAew-misc:Depends+AH0-
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 DonCoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. DonCoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. DonCoin Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, doncoind, and the CLI tool
 doncoin-cli to interact with the daemon.

Package: doncoin-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: +ACQAew-shlibs:Depends+AH0-, +ACQAew-misc:Depends+AH0-
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 DonCoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. DonCoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. DonCoin Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides DonCoin-Qt, a GUI for DonCoin based on Qt.

Package: doncoin-tx
Architecture: any
Depends: +ACQAew-shlibs:Depends+AH0-, +ACQAew-misc:Depends+AH0-
Description: peer-to-peer digital currency - standalone transaction tool
 DonCoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. DonCoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. DonCoin Core
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides doncoin-tx, a command-line transaction creation
 tool which can be used without a doncoin daemon.  Some means of
 exchanging minimal transaction data with peers is still required.
